snippet.title: Bomberman B-Daman (Super Famicom) - Game Play
snippet.description:
Bomberman B-Daman is an Action game, developed by AI and published by Hudson, which was released in Japan in 1996.

This is game play footage of Bomberman B-Daman for the Super Famicom
